msg: Update the way the Form is named:
1) A default form will not have the name set.  This used to be set to either a generated
2) If the tagId is set, then we will set the name and id to the same value in HTML
and will set only the id in XHTML.

tagId isn't set)  The name will be a generated name.
This cause a huge amount of test results to be updated.
